            _done: null,
            get done() {
                if(!this._done) {
                    this._done = new Array();
                }
                return this._done;
            },
            addAnimations: function() {
                var style = document.createElement('style');
                style.type = 'text/css';
                style.innerHTML = 'object,embed{\
                -webkit-animation-duration:.001s;-webkit-animation-name:playerInserted;\
                -ms-animation-duration:.001s;-ms-animation-name:playerInserted;\
                -o-animation-duration:.001s;-o-animation-name:playerInserted;\
                animation-duration:.001s;animation-name:playerInserted;}\
                @-webkit-keyframes playerInserted{from{opacity:0.99;}to{opacity:1;}}\
                @-ms-keyframes playerInserted{from{opacity:0.99;}to{opacity:1;}}\
                @-o-keyframes playerInserted{from{opacity:0.99;}to{opacity:1;}}\
                @keyframes playerInserted{from{opacity:0.99;}to{opacity:1;}}';
                document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(style);
            },
            animationsHandler: function(e) {
                if(e.animationName === 'playerInserted') {
                    this.replace(e.target);
                }
            },
            replace: function(elem) {
                if (/http:\/\/v.youku.com\/v_show\/.*/.test(window.location.href)){
                    var tag = document.getElementById("playerBox").getAttribute("player")
                    if (tag == "adt"){
                        console.log("adt adv")
                        return;
                    }
                }
                if(this.done.indexOf(elem) != -1) return;
                this.done.push(elem);
                var player = elem.data || elem.src;
                if(!player) return;
                var i, find, replace = false;
                for(i in this.rules) {
                    find = this.rules[i]['find'];
                    if(find.test(player)) {
                        replace = this.rules[i]['replace'];
                        if('function' === typeof this.rules[i]['preHandle']) {
                            this.rules[i]['preHandle'].bind(this, elem, find, replace, player)();
                        }else{
                            this.reallyReplace.bind(this, elem, find, replace)();
                        }
                        break;
                    }
                }
            },
            reallyReplace: function(elem, find, replace) {
                elem.data && (elem.data = elem.data.replace(find, replace)) || elem.src && ((elem.src = elem.src.replace(find, replace)) && (elem.style.display = 'block'));
                var b = elem.querySelector("param[name='movie']");
                this.reloadPlugin(elem);
            },
            reloadPlugin: function(elem) {
                var nextSibling = elem.nextSibling;
                var parentNode = elem.parentNode;
                parentNode.removeChild(elem);
                var newElem = elem.cloneNode(true);
                this.done.push(newElem);
                if(nextSibling) {
                    parentNode.insertBefore(newElem, nextSibling);
                } else {
                    parentNode.appendChild(newElem);
                }
            },
            init: function() {
                var desc = navigator.mimeTypes['application/x-shockwave-flash'].description.toLowerCase();
                /*if(desc.indexOf('adobe')>-1){
                 delete this.rules["iqiyi_1"];
                 delete this.rules["iqiyi_2"];
                 }*/
                if(document.URL.indexOf('tv.sohu.com')<=0){
                    delete this.rules["sohu"];
                }
                var handler = this.animationsHandler.bind(this);
                document.body.addEventListener('webkitAnimationStart', handler, false);
                document.body.addEventListener('msAnimationStart', handler, false);
                document.body.addEventListener('oAnimationStart', handler, false);
                document.body.addEventListener('animationstart', handler, false);
                this.addAnimations();
            }
        };
        new A().init();
    })();
}

    <script type="text/javascript" id="spaui-script">
      if (!window.P) {window.P = window.ASPP;}

      
      
      if (!P.guardFatal) {
        P.guardFatal = function (name, callback) {
          if ( !callback ) {
            callback = name;
            name = undefined;
          }

          var join = function(delimiter, a, b, c) {
            var firstTwo = a && b ? a + delimiter + b : a || b;
            return c ? join(delimiter, firstTwo, c) : firstTwo;
          };

          return function guarded () {
            try {
              var result = callback.apply(this, arguments);
              return result;
            }
            catch (err) {
              var console = window.console;
              if (console && console.error) {
                console.error(join(String.fromCharCode(10),
                  join(": ", name, err.message),
                  err.stack || err
                ));
              }
            }
          };
        }
      }

<script>
  var athena = (function() {'use strict';
	  var cfg = {
	    pairs: window.location.href.split(/[\?&]+/),
	    title: '',
	    url: window.location.pathname.split(/\/ref=/)[0],
	    debugArgs: '',
	    override: {
	      title: 'spaui',
	      url: 'spaui-url',
	      spauiDebug: 'spauiDebug',
	      auiDebug: 'auiDebug',
	      auiReset: 'auiReset'
	    }
	  };
	  var method = {
	    init: function () {
	      method.hydrate();
	      method.override();
	      method.sniff();
	      //method.vanilla();
	    },
	    hydrate: function () {
	      if (document.getElementsByTagName('title').length > 0) {
		cfg.title = encodeURIComponent(document.getElementsByTagName('title')[0].innerHTML);
	      }
	    },
	    override: function () {
	      var len = cfg.pairs.length, i;
	      for (i = 0; i < len; i++) {
	        var value = cfg.pairs[i].split(/=/);
	        if (value[0] === cfg.override.title) {
	          cfg.title = value[1];
	        }
	        if (value[0] === cfg.override.url) {
	          cfg.url = value[1];
	        }
	        if (value[0] === cfg.override.spauiDebug) {
	          cfg.debugArgs = cfg.debugArgs + '&spauiDebug=1&auiDebug=1&auiReset=1';
	        }
	        if (value[0] === cfg.override.auiDebug) {
	          cfg.debugArgs = cfg.debugArgs + '&auiDebug=1';
	        }
	        if (value[0] === cfg.override.auiReset) {
	          cfg.debugArgs = cfg.debugArgs + '&auiReset=1';
	        }
	      }
	    },
	    sniff: function () {
              try {
                if (typeof P !== 'undefined' && typeof P.when !== 'undefined') {
	          P.when('A').execute(function (A) {
	            method.ready(A.$);
	          });
	        } else if (typeof $ !== 'undefined') {//we have jquery. < 1.4 use vanilla();
	          if (parseInt($.fn.jquery.substr(0,1), 10) === 1) {//major version is 1
	            if (parseInt($.fn.jquery.substr(2,1), 10) < 4) {//minor is < 4
	              method.vanilla();
	            } else {//minor is >= 4
	              method.ready($);
	            }
	          } else {//major is > 1
	            method.ready($);
	          }
	        } else {//we don't
	          method.vanilla();
  	        }
              } catch(ex) {
                method.vanilla();
              }
  	    },
	    ready: function (ref) {
	      var $ = ref;
	      $.get('/help/inline/main/athena-widget?' + 'pageTitle=' + cfg.title + '&pageUrl=' + cfg.url + cfg.debugArgs, function (data) {
	        $('#athena-widget-container').html(data);
	      });
	    },
	    vanilla: function () {
	      var xhr;
	      if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {//modern
	        xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
	      } else if (window.ActiveXObject) {//vintage
	        try {xhr = new ActiveXObject('Msxml2.XMLHTTP');}
	        catch (e) {
	          try {xhr = new ActiveXObject('Microsoft.XMLHTTP');}//retro
	          catch (e) {}
	        }
	      }
	      if (!xhr) {
	        return;//fail
	      }
	      xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {
	        if (xhr.readyState === 4) {
	          if (xhr.status === 200) {
	            var awc = document.getElementById('athena-widget-container');
	            awc.innerHTML = xhr.responseText;
	            method.scripty();
	          }
	        }
	      };
	      xhr.open('GET', '/help/inline/main/athena-widget?' + 'pageTitle=' + cfg.title + '&pageUrl=' + cfg.url + cfg.debugArgs);
	      xhr.send();
	    },
	    scripty: function () {
	      var scripts = ['aspp', 'load', 'state', 'script'];
	      var len = scripts.length, i;
	      for (i = 0; i < len; i++) {
	        if (!document.getElementById('spaui-' + scripts[i])) {
	          break;//ie8
	        }
	        var script = document.createElement('script');
	        if (scripts[i] === 'state') {
	          script.text = '[' + document.getElementById('spaui-' + scripts[i]).innerHTML + ']';//add json as array
	        } else {
	          script.text = document.getElementById('spaui-' + scripts[i]).innerHTML;
	        }
	        document.body.appendChild(script);
	      }
	    }
	  };
	  var api = {
	    init: method.init
	  }
	  return api;
	})();
	athena.init();
</script>

<script>
function clickclear(thisfield, defaulttext) {
  thisfield.style.color = "#000000";
  if (thisfield.value == defaulttext) {
    thisfield.value = "";
  }
}

function clickrestore(thisfield, defaulttext) {
  if (thisfield.value == "") {
    thisfield.style.color = "#808080";
    thisfield.value = defaulttext;
  }
}
</script>

	    aanSlot   = "seller-app-orders";

	var getUrlParam = function(name){
	      var results = new RegExp('[\\?&]' + name + '=([^&#]*)').exec(window.location.href);
	      return results!==null?results[1]:null;
	};

	if(getUrlParam('slotoverride') !== null) {
	    aanSlot = getUrlParam('slotoverride');
	}

	var getScript = function(scriptUrl, callback){
	    jQuery.ajax({
		url: scriptUrl,
		data: null,
		dataType: 'script',
		cache: true,
		success: callback
	    });
	}; 
	getScript(baseUrl + urlSuffix, function(){
        if(typeof d16g === 'undefined') {
          return;
        }
	    d16g.requestAanAd({
		  elemId: "ad-top",
		baseUrl: baseUrl,
		afterOnload: true,
		  client: client,
		  pt: "sellercentral",
		  slot: aanSlot,
		  pt2: "sellercentral"
	    });
	});
    });
});
 
</script>

    </td>
  </tr>
</tbody></table>

<script type="text/javascript">
function changeLanguageFooterWithRefTag(list, switchLanguageURL) {
    var language = list.options[list.selectedIndex].value,
    location = encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);

    if (language) {
        window.location.href = "https://sellercentral.amazon.com/gp/switch-language.html/ref=ag_swlang_foot_myo?ie=UTF8&formSubmitted=true" + "&language=" + language + "&location=" + location;
    }
}
</script>

      if (!window.P) {window.P = window.ASPP;}

      
      
      if (!P.guardFatal) {
        P.guardFatal = function (name, callback) {
          if ( !callback ) {
            callback = name;
            name = undefined;
          }

          var join = function(delimiter, a, b, c) {
            var firstTwo = a && b ? a + delimiter + b : a || b;
            return c ? join(delimiter, firstTwo, c) : firstTwo;
          };

          return function guarded () {
            try {
              var result = callback.apply(this, arguments);
              return result;
            }
            catch (err) {
              var console = window.console;
              if (console && console.error) {
                console.error(join(String.fromCharCode(10),
                  join(": ", name, err.message),
                  err.stack || err
                ));
              }
            }
          };
        }
      }
